{
  "stem": "1502.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 116,
      "text": "And they're screaming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 117,
      "text": "And it was extremely, extremely-- uncomfortable is not the word.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 118,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 119,
      "text": "Because ?] very difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 120,
      "text": "And we stayed in that basement, if I remember correctly, for two days and two nights.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 121,
      "text": "If someone had to go to the bathroom, you had to-- you had to knock on the gates.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 122,
      "text": "There was a gate, like same way as a jail cell.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 123,
      "text": "And the SS would take you to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 124,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] To stay in that-- in that basement-- we were looking forward to be taken out and taken to Mechelen, like a-- like freedom.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 125,
      "text": "Because it was extremely painful to stay in that place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 126,
      "text": "After-- after two days and they accumulated enough Jews, that is the only time and the first time that I have seen Jacques the Informer.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 127,
      "text": "I looked out from the-- through the gate, and there he was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 128,
      "text": "He came to the cellar to look at the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 129,
      "text": "Because there must have been some Jews that he caught.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 130,
      "text": "And then they took us-- from the-- from the cellar, they took us into a truck, a-- I guess a military truck.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 131,
      "text": "They were two guards with rifles and bayonets at the two corners of the truck, and also two guards with the driver in the front.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 132,
      "text": "Truck was full of Jews, men, women, children that were caught recently.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 133,
      "text": "And the truck proceeded to Mechelen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 134,
      "text": "When we arrived in Mechelen, there was a big door, like a gate, but, you know, in like in the ancient-- the ancient forts, with a big door.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 135,
      "text": "They opened up the door wide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 136,
      "text": "And the truck rolled into the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 137,
      "text": "The procedure was, when the Jews that were caught arrived to Mechelen, everything was brutal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 138,
      "text": "So, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 139,
      "text": "They would kick people off the truck.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
